Package smarthome.mapper

Class RoomDTO

java.lang.Object
org.springframework.hateoas.RepresentationModel<RoomDTO>
smarthome.mapper.RoomDTO
public class RoomDTO extends org.springframework.hateoas.RepresentationModel<RoomDTO>
Data Transfer Object (DTO) for room information. Encapsulates data for a room including the house name, room name, floor, and dimensions.
